A Simple Annotation Editor
- Press 'Left-Arrow' / 'Right-Arrow' to move cursor
- Click anywhere to move cursor
- Press 'Space' to add separator
- Press 'Delete' to remove separator

Setup
1. Install node [https://nodejs.org/]
2. Install npm [https://www.npmjs.com/]
3. npm install
4. [in one terminal] npm run start
5. [in another terminal] sudo python -m SimpleHTTPServer 8080
6. Open browser and hit http://localhost:8080/index.html